## Push Summary — skrptiq-cli (main)

### What shipped
Refactored all slash commands to use explicit subcommands — bare commands now show usage instead of silently doing one thing.

**Pattern:** `/hub` shows usage, `/hub list` lists imports, `/hub search` searches. Applied across all multi-action commands:
- `/hub list|search|import|update`
- `/profile list|show|use`
- `/dials show|set`
- `/mcp list|connect|disconnect|tools`
- `/providers list|add`
- `/workspace show|set`
- `/tags list`
- `/config show|set`
- `/runs list`

Autocomplete registry updated to match — typing `/hub` shows `list`, `search`, `import`, `update` as completions.

